,0,'pt','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wc4IkCXCZyboTRY0ye8lwbqRF2f.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:32',0,'Premium','Series'),(854,'The Dick Cavett Show','The Dick Cavett Show has been the title of several talk shows hosted by Dick Cavett on various television networks.',1968,90,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uDkndfnwbEGeSY4YmZbTRg4U5RQ.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-2i3A2Fb5mw','2025-04-05 15:59:34',0,'Premium','Series'),(855,'Chronicles of the Sun','Claire is surprised when she gets arrested for the murder of her childhood friend after she returns to Montpellier.',2018,26,'fr','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t6jVlbPMtZOJoAOfeoR4yQmnjXM.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:37',0,'Premium','Series'),(856,'Goede Tijden, Slechte Tijden','Goede tijden, slechte tijden, also known as GTST, is the longest-running Dutch soap opera,  revolving around the lives of the families Alberts, Sanders, De Jong, Van Houten and Bouwhuis. It all takes place in the fictional town of Meerdijk.',1990,30,'nl','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p1oXgtJ0q0wAcEp3tHA5DpiynxL.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:39',0,'Free','Series'),(857,'CBeebies Bedtime Stories','Join a host of different celebrities for a different story read each night just before bedtime.',2009,0,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/b0ScjqTEs9XNpGsFueXdwPbWHtC.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:41',0,'VIP','Series'),(858,'Ninja Boy Rantaro','Rantarō, Shinbei and Kirimaru are ninja  apprentices in the Ninja Gakuen, where first grade ones are called  \"Nintamas\". They must learn  everything a ninja must know, but as for our heroes, money, food or  playing are more interesting. The series show the everyday adventures of  our heroes.',1993,30,'ja','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xdnt8Dx5Z8Ad78GfqSSsk9kv4tB.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:42',0,'VIP','Series'),(859,'I\'ve Got a Secret','A panel tries to determine a contestant\'s secret: something that is unusual, amazing, embarrassing, or humorous about that person.',1952,30,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yMGxV37D6Jt3Len7q8QocLJJ5E3.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:44',0,'Free','Series'),(860,'LIVE with Kelly and Mark','A morning talk show with A-list celebrity guests, top-notch performances and one-of-a-kind segments that are unrivaled on daytime television, plus spontaneous, hilarious and unpredictable talk.',1988,44,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/l5y8egG27p2fSTyq8s21SQMmQLy.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:47',0,'VIP','Series'),(861,'NPR Tiny Desk Concerts','Intimate musical performances, recorded live at the desk of All Songs Considered host Bob Boilen.',2008,17,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sJ6HdzajIVkC5G2kRROhNu8at43.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:49',0,'VIP','Series'),(862,'The One Show','A topical magazine-style daily television programme broadcast live on BBC One.',2006,29,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7QpzCej3Lwrsnx5A8FePYsUCIzf.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:51',0,'Free','Series'),(863,'Coronation Street','The residents of Coronation Street are ordinary, working-class people, and the show follows them through regular social and family interactions at home, in the workplace, and in their local pub, the Rovers Return Inn. Britain\'s longest-running soap.',1960,24,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5x1HXqYqPyYw7oc7Isu1lvVmwRP.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:56',0,'VIP','Series'),(864,'Home and Away','Home and Away is set in the fictional town of Summer Bay, a coastal town in New South Wales, and follows the personal and professional lives of the people living in the area. The show initially focused on the Fletcher family, Pippa and Tom Fletcher and their five foster children Frank Morgan, Carly Morris, Steven Matheson, Lynn Davenport and Sally Keating, who would go on to become one of the show\'s longest-running characters. The show also originally and currently focuses on the Stewart family. During the early 2000s, the central storylines focused on the Sutherlands and later, the Hunters. Home and Away had proved popular when it premiered in 1988 and had risen to become a hit in Australia, and after only a few weeks, the show tackled its first major and disturbing storyline, the rape of Carly Morris; it was one of the first shows to feature such storylines during the early timeslot. H&A has tackled many adult-themed and controversial storylines; something rarely found in its restricted timeslot.',1988,21,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vn0eKMiG69bhQtxb7qLRo8SSqu5.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 15:59:58',0,'VIP','Series'),(865,'Prisoner: Cell Block H','Prisoner is an Australian soap opera that is set in the Wentworth Detention Centre, a fictional women\'s prison.',1979,55,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9OSK44nb6ZZkMxkX6SLeQszVFke.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 16:00:00',0,'VIP','Series'),(866,'Elefant, Tiger & Co.','',2003,25,'de','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zeqpdXFVIV2FXaug7tib1N2dNlc.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 16:00:03',0,'Free','Series'),(867,'Volle Kanne','',1999,90,'de','TV-14',NULL,NULL,'2025-04-05 16:00:06',0,'Premium','Series'),(868,'The Merv Griffin Show','The Merv Griffin Show is an American television talk show, starring Merv Griffin. The series ran from October 1, 1962 to March 29, 1963 on NBC, September 20, 1965 to August 15, 1969 in first-run syndication, from August 18, 1969 to February 11, 1972 at 11:30 PM ET weeknights on CBS and again in first-run syndication from February 14, 1972 to September 5, 1986.',1962,60,'en','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pF9rFdF6Gd4dNJ0Rh4mFsaFTi3m.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 16:00:07',0,'Free','Series'),(869,'BANGTAN BOMB','Bangtan Bomb are short videos of BTS released on their YouTube channel.',2013,0,'ko','TV-14','https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/i01uYYJoovqILhexlYA6E1CHh56.jpg',NULL,'2025-04-05 16:00:09',0,'VIP','Series'),(870,'Real Time with Bill Maher','Each week Bill Maher surrounds himself with a panel of guests which include politic